
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link href="/css/proj3.css" rel = "stylesheet" type="text/css">

  <body>

    <div style="padding-left:16px">
      <h2>Tropical Fish Emporium</h2>
        <p>Here customers, employees, sales, and products can be added to the database.</p>
          <form method = "post">
<!--CUSTOMERS-->
      <fieldset>
        <legend>Add Customer Here:</legend>
          <label>First Name:
            <input type ="text" name ="CfirstName">
          </label><br><br>
          <label>Last Name:
            <input type ="text" name ="ClastName">
          </label><br><br>
          <label>E-mail Address:
            <input type ="text" name ="Cemail">
          </label><br><br>
          <label>Member Since:
            <input type ="date" name ="CmemberSince">
          </label><br><br>
          <button onclick="confirmCust();return false;">Submit</button>
            <div id="custTy"></div>
      </fieldset>

<!--EMPLOYEES-->
      <fieldset>
        <legend>Add Employee Here:</legend>
  			   <label>First Name:
             <input type ="text" name ="EfirstName">
           </label><br><br>
  			   <label>Last Name:
             <input type ="text" name ="ElastName">
           </label><br><br>
           <label>Store ID:
            <input type ="number" name ="Estore_id">
          </label><br><br>
           <label>Title:
            <input type ="text" name ="Etitle">
          </label><br><br>
  			   <label>Shift Start-Time:
             <input type ="time" name ="EstartTime">
           </label><br><br>
  			   <label>Shift End-Time:
             <input type ="time" name ="EendTime">
           </label><br><br>
  			   <label>Hourly Rate:
             <input type ="number" name ="EhourlyRate">
           </label><br><br>
  			   <label>Part-Time?</label>
  				   <select name = "EpartTime">
  					        <option value = "TRUE" selected> Yes</option>
  					        <option value = "FALSE" selected> No</option>
             </select><br><br>
            <button onclick="confirmEmp();return false;">Submit</button>
             <div id="empTy"></div>
      </fieldset>

<!--PRODUCTS-->
      <fieldset>
        <legend>Add Product Here:</legend>
          <p>Adding a product will add a product record to the database, and will also add a row to the intersection table
          "products_sales." The primary key of the product record will be a <strong>foreign key</strong> in the product_sales table.</p>
          <label>Product Name:
            <input type ="text" name ="Pname">
          </label><br><br>
          <label>Price
            <input type ="price" name ="Pprice">
          </label><br><br>
          <button onclick="confirmProd();return false;">Submit</button>
            <div id="prodTy"></div>
      </fieldset>

<!--SALES-->
      <fieldset>
        <legend>Add Sale Here:</legend>
          <p>Adding a sale will add a sale record to the database, and will also add a row to the intersection table
            "products_sales." The primary key of the sale record will be a <strong>foreign key</strong> in the product_sales table.</p>
          <label>Employee ID (who comlpeted the sale):
            <input type ="id" name ="SemployeeID">
          </label><br><br>
          <label>Customer ID (optional):
            <select id="customerID">
              <option value="3">3: James Anderson</option>
              <option value="12">12: Sally Brands</option>
              <option value="5">5: Andrew Clos</option>
              <option value="1">1: Haley Woehrle</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <strong>customer ID will dynamically populate with all customers using a SELECT query on the `Customers` table.</strong><br><br>
          <label>Transaction Date:
            <input type ="date" name ="StransactionDate">
          </label><br><br>
          <label>Purchase Total (including tax):
            <input type ="price" name ="StotalPurchase">
          </label><br><br>
          <label>Number of distinct products:
            <input type ="number" name ="SnumProds" id="numProds" value="1">
          </label><br><br>
            <button onclick="confirmSal();showProds();return false;">Submit</button>
              <div id="salTy"></div>
      </fieldset>
        <div id="sales_prods"></div>
    </form>
    </div>
